            "text": "<strong>VORES SPONSORER</strong><p><strong>Guld</strong><br/>Siteimprove A/S, Crowne Plaza Copenhagen Tower A/S, Nordea Bank Danmark A/S, Opel Danmark A/S, Flügger A/S, Gjensidige Forsikring A/S</p><p><strong>Sølv</strong><br/>Danhostel Copenhagen Amager</p><p><strong>Bronze</strong><br/>Fujitsu A/S, HC Container A/S, Anders Andersens Rengøring, Ferring Pharmaceuticals A/S, Rosenberg Bogtryk ApS, Cowi A/S, Amager Fiskehus ApS, Freetrailer ApS, Uni-Safe A/S, Hempel A/S, Øens Ejendomsadminstration A/S, Arbejdernes Landsbank A/S, Tårnby Forsyning Varme A/S, Botium A/S, Admiral Hotel, Lauren Erhvervsrengøring ApS, Orloff Firmatøj A/S, Delfin Vask A/S, Haldor Torpsøe A/S, Maxi Zoo Danmark A/S, Dykkercentret ApS, Beckett-Fonden, Cargill Nordic A/S, Tømrerfirmaet Bjørn Svendsen A/S</p><p><strong>Ambassadører</strong><br/>Cafax Amager, Poppi Dyrecenter Østerbro ApS, Camping Danmark A/S, Quality Airport Hotel Dan A/S, Dragør Fort, Dynateam CRM A/S, Sepio A/S, Africa Tours, BankNordik, Cabinn Hotels</p>"
